{"tid":1863940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完7婆個記招有無人好L嬲？","createTime":"2020-02-05T11:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T16:24:51.000Z","uid":132217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4860a053ca181c75d5f840c8ef7767c8e73d15d2","tid":1863940,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"明知條友又係spin 我地<br />\n<br />\n措施又係要差兩日先實施<br />\n講到好似做左好多野，同好合理咁，但其實咩都無細節的措施<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地本身要<br />\n<br />\n封關<br />\n香港返黎就隔離14日<br />\n<br />\n而家就<br />\n<br />\n關可以繼續過<br />\n唔知細節的檢疫設施，分分鐘係在家隔離14日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢又心諗做到繼續開比上面醫病，讓左咁多步大家總唔會繼續咁一致支持勇武手足啦，分化成功今次仲唔又考第一？<br />\n<br />\n明明無讓過步，扮下道歉，又覺得好多人醫護會比佢呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就好L嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80eeb57b006a742b4be81d596bfb67eed8ae28d0","tid":1863940,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"唔推啦，有人一樣咁嬲先入黎圍下爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8fba8aac52d04b7b51ef141b61d297d1020353","tid":1863940,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"嬲左8個月啦"},{"pid":"276145e6456e62455ed7d7b812a88fe617e95080","tid":1863940,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嬲咗半年幾重係嬲</span>"},{"pid":"c306699af679d468a5864e25e082ddbf305a686b","tid":1863940,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8fba8aac52d04b7b51ef141b61d297d1020353","tid":1863940,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"嬲左8個月啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"呢個當然，睇完又再嬲嬲多D"},{"pid":"e1dd527d65780a19d52b752e84f7157efcb3faea","tid":1863940,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,